snippet.title: Hololive Sings - YOASOBI - Racing into the Night (Yoru ni Kakeru 夜に駆ける) (30 Covers)
snippet.description:
Since me and broke gang don't have tickets to today's Bloom concert, I mixed 30 covers of "Yoru ni Kakeru" into a mini performance! To everyone who attended today's concert, I hope it was well worth the wait, and it becomes a memory you'll never forget!
